#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.53"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.53:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.53:0.2"
msgid "6. Puññābhisandavagga"
msgstr "6. Overflowing Merit"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.53:0.3"
msgid "53. Paṭhamasaṃvāsasutta"
msgstr "53. Living Together (1st)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.53:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā antarā ca madhuraṃ antarā ca verañjaṃ "
"addhānamaggappaṭipanno hoti."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was traveling along the road between Madhura and "
"Verañja,"

msgctxt "an4.53:1.2"
msgid ""
"Sambahulāpi kho gahapatī ca gahapatāniyo ca antarā ca madhuraṃ antarā ca "
"verañjaṃ addhānamaggappaṭipannā honti."
msgstr "as were several householders, both women and men."

#. VAR: () → (paññatte āsane) (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "an4.53:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā maggā okkamma aññatarasmiṃ rukkhamūle () nisīdi."
msgstr "The Buddha left the road and sat at the root of a tree,"

#. VAR: Addasaṃsu → addassuṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.53:1.4"
msgid ""
"Addasaṃsu kho gahapatī ca gahapatāniyo ca bhagavantaṃ aññatarasmiṃ "
"rukkhamūle nisinnaṃ."
msgstr "where the householders saw him."

msgctxt "an4.53:1.5"
msgid ""
"Disvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā "
"ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinne kho te gahapatī ca gahapatāniyo ca "
"bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"They went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said "
"to them:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.53:2.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, gahapatayo, saṃvāsā."
msgstr "“Householders, there are four ways of living together."

msgctxt "an4.53:2.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.53:2.3"
msgid ""
"Chavo chavāya saddhiṃ saṃvasati, chavo deviyā saddhiṃ saṃvasati, devo "
"chavāya saddhiṃ saṃvasati, devo deviyā saddhiṃ saṃvasati."
msgstr ""
"~A male zombie living with a female zombie; ~a male zombie living with a "
"goddess; ~a god living with a female zombie; ~a god living with a goddess."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.58"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.53:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, gahapatayo, chavo chavāya saddhiṃ saṃvasati?"
msgstr "And how does a male zombie live with a female zombie?"

msgctxt "an4.53:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, gahapatayo, sāmiko hoti pāṇātipātī adinnādāyī kāmesumicchācārī "
"musāvādī surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhāyī dussīlo pāpadhammo "
"maccheramalapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati akkosakaparibhāsako "
"samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when the husband kills living creatures, steals, commits sexual "
"misconduct, lies, and uses alcoholic drinks that cause negligence. He’s "
"unethical, of bad character, living at home with his heart full of the stain "
"of stinginess, abusing and insulting ascetics and brahmins."

msgctxt "an4.53:3.3"
msgid ""
"bhariyāpissa hoti pāṇātipātinī adinnādāyinī kāmesumicchācārinī musāvādinī "
"surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhāyinī dussīlā pāpadhammā maccheramalapariyuṭṭhitena "
"cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati akkosikaparibhāsikā samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ."
msgstr "And the wife is also … unethical, of bad character …"

msgctxt "an4.53:3.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, gahapatayo, chavo chavāya saddhiṃ saṃvasati."
msgstr "That’s how a male zombie lives with a female zombie."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.53:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, gahapatayo, chavo deviyā saddhiṃ saṃvasati?"
msgstr "And how does a male zombie live with a goddess?"

msgctxt "an4.53:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, gahapatayo, sāmiko hoti pāṇātipātī adinnādāyī kāmesumicchācārī "
"musāvādī surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhāyī dussīlo pāpadhammo "
"maccheramalapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati akkosakaparibhāsako "
"samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ;"
msgstr "It’s when the husband … is unethical, of bad character …"

msgctxt "an4.53:4.3"
msgid ""
"bhariyā khvassa hoti pāṇātipātā paṭiviratā adinnādānā paṭiviratā "
"kāmesumicchācārā paṭiviratā musāvādā paṭiviratā surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā "
"paṭiviratā sīlavatī kalyāṇadhammā vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ "
"ajjhāvasati anakkosikaparibhāsikā samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"But the wife doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, "
"lie, or use alcoholic drinks that cause negligence. She’s ethical, of good "
"character, living at home with her heart rid of the stain of stinginess, not "
"abusing and insulting ascetics and brahmins."

msgctxt "an4.53:4.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, gahapatayo, chavo deviyā saddhiṃ saṃvasati."
msgstr "That’s how a male zombie lives with a goddess."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.53:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, gahapatayo, devo chavāya saddhiṃ saṃvasati?"
msgstr "And how does a god live with a female zombie?"

msgctxt "an4.53:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, gahapatayo, sāmiko hoti pāṇātipātā paṭivirato adinnādānā paṭivirato "
"kāmesumicchācārā paṭivirato musāvādā paṭivirato surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā "
"paṭivirato sīlavā kalyāṇadhammo vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ "
"ajjhāvasati anakkosakaparibhāsako samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ;"
msgstr "It’s when the husband … is ethical, of good character …"

msgctxt "an4.53:5.3"
msgid ""
"bhariyā khvassa hoti pāṇātipātinī … pe … surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhāyinī "
"dussīlā pāpadhammā maccheramalapariyuṭṭhitena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati "
"akkosikaparibhāsikā samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ."
msgstr "But the wife … is unethical, of bad character …"

msgctxt "an4.53:5.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, gahapatayo, devo chavāya saddhiṃ saṃvasati."
msgstr "That’s how a god lives with a female zombie."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.59"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.53:6.1"
msgid "Kathañca, gahapatayo, devo deviyā saddhiṃ saṃvasati?"
msgstr "And how does a god live with a goddess?"

msgctxt "an4.53:6.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, gahapatayo, sāmiko hoti pāṇātipātā paṭivirato … pe … sīlavā "
"kalyāṇadhammo vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ ajjhāvasati "
"anakkosakaparibhāsako samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ;"
msgstr "It’s when the husband … is ethical, of good character …"

msgctxt "an4.53:6.3"
msgid ""
"bhariyāpissa hoti pāṇātipātā paṭiviratā … pe … surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā "
"paṭiviratā sīlavatī kalyāṇadhammā vigatamalamaccherena cetasā agāraṃ "
"ajjhāvasati anakkosikaparibhāsikā samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ."
msgstr "And the wife is also … ethical, of good character …"

msgctxt "an4.53:6.4"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, gahapatayo, devo deviyā saddhiṃ saṃvasati."
msgstr "That’s how a god lives with a goddess."

msgctxt "an4.53:6.5"
msgid "Ime kho, gahapatayo, cattāro saṃvāsāti."
msgstr "These are the four ways of living together."

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "an4.53:7.1"
msgid "Ubho ca honti dussīlā,"
msgstr "When both are unethical,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:7.2"
msgid "kadariyā paribhāsakā;"
msgstr "miserly and abusive,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:7.3"
msgid "Te honti jānipatayo,"
msgstr "then wife and husband"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:7.4"
msgid "chavā saṃvāsamāgatā."
msgstr "live together as zombies."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "an4.53:8.1"
msgid "Sāmiko hoti dussīlo,"
msgstr "When the husband is unethical,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:8.2"
msgid "kadariyo paribhāsako;"
msgstr "miserly and abusive,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:8.3"
msgid "Bhariyā sīlavatī hoti,"
msgstr "but the wife is ethical,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:8.4"
msgid "vadaññū vītamaccharā;"
msgstr "kind, rid of stinginess,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:8.5"
msgid "Sāpi devī saṃvasati,"
msgstr "she’s a goddess living"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:8.6"
msgid "chavena patinā saha."
msgstr "with a zombie for a husband."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "an4.53:9.1"
msgid "Sāmiko sīlavā hoti,"
msgstr "When the husband is ethical,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:9.2"
msgid "vadaññū vītamaccharo;"
msgstr "kind, rid of stinginess,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:9.3"
msgid "Bhariyā hoti dussīlā,"
msgstr "but the wife is unethical,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:9.4"
msgid "kadariyā paribhāsikā;"
msgstr "miserly and abusive,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:9.5"
msgid "Sāpi chavā saṃvasati,"
msgstr "she’s a zombie living"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:9.6"
msgid "devena patinā saha."
msgstr "with a god for a husband."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "an4.53:10.1"
msgid "Ubho saddhā vadaññū ca,"
msgstr "When both are faithful and kind,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:10.2"
msgid "saññatā dhammajīvino;"
msgstr "restrained, living properly,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:10.3"
msgid "Te honti jānipatayo,"
msgstr "then wife and husband"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:10.4"
msgid "aññamaññaṃ piyaṃvadā."
msgstr "say nice things to each other."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
#. VAR: Atthāsaṃ pacurā → atthā sampacurā (bj, s1-3, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.53:11.1"
msgid "Atthāsaṃ pacurā honti,"
msgstr "They get all the things they need,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: phāsukaṃ → phāsatthaṃ (bj) | vāsatthaṃ (pts1)
msgctxt "an4.53:11.2"
msgid "phāsukaṃ upajāyati;"
msgstr "so they live at ease."

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:11.3"
msgid "Amittā dummanā honti,"
msgstr "Their enemies are downhearted,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:11.4"
msgid "ubhinnaṃ samasīlinaṃ."
msgstr "when both are equal in ethics."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "an4.53:12.1"
msgid "Idha dhammaṃ caritvāna,"
msgstr "Having practiced the teaching here,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:12.2"
msgid "samasīlabbatā ubho;"
msgstr "both equal in precepts and observances,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:12.3"
msgid "Nandino devalokasmiṃ,"
msgstr "they delight in the heavenly realm,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.53:12.4"
msgid "modanti kāmakāmino”ti."
msgstr "enjoying all the pleasures they desire.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.53:12.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
